# Markdown File Creation Policy

**NEVER create .md files unless the user explicitly asks for them.**

This includes:
- README.md
- Documentation files
- API documentation
- Implementation summaries
- Guide files
- Any other .md files

## Exception

Only create .md files when the user specifically requests:
- "Create a README"
- "Document this in markdown"
- "Make a .md file for..."

## Why

Users prefer to control when documentation is created. Proactively generating documentation files clutters the workspace and may not align with their documentation strategy.
